* SNAG
  This set of ansible scripts to setup the infrastructure at VLEAD.

* Pre-requisite
  Following packages should be installed on the machine which is
  expected to run the output generated by tangling the sources stored.
  in this repository:
  - ansible

* Set hosts
  Copy the src/hosts/default.sample to src/hosts/default and edit the
  hosts values.

* How to run
  To build both sources and documentation use make.  Then build
  directory can be copied to ansible server and executed with
  #+BEGIN_EXAMPLE
  ansible-playbook -i hosts/default site.yaml
  #+END_EXAMPLE

